<p>A <code>NetPromoterScorePickerButton</code> is one button inside
  a <a href="/components/net-promoter-score-picker/"><code>NetPromoterScorePicker</code></a>.
  Each button is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  <code>data-value</code> (0–10) and <code>data-category</code>
  (detractor / passive / promoter) that the example CSS uses to
  colour the button red, yellow, or green.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/net-promoter-score-picker/">Picker
  demo</a> for composed examples.</p>
